eight="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Deftones-and-System-Of-A-Down.-Credit-Barry-Brecheisen-and-Daniel-Knighton-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Deftones 和向下的系统。图片来源：Barry Brecheisen 和 Daniel Knighton，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Deftones-and-System-Of-A-Down.-Credit-Barry-Brecheisen-and-Daniel-Knighton-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Deftones-and-System-Of-A-Down.-Credit-Barry-Brecheisen-and-Daniel-Knighton-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Deftones-and-System-Of-A-Down.-Credit-Barry-Brecheisen-and-Daniel-Knighton-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Deftones-and-System-Of-A-Down.-Credit-Barry-Brecheisen-and-Daniel-Knighton-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Deftones-and-System-Of-A-Down.-Credit-Barry-Brecheisen-and-Daniel-Knighton-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Deftones-and-System-Of-A-Down.-Credit-Barry-Brecheisen-and-Daniel-Knighton-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>上周末， <a href="/artists/Deftones">Deftones</a>与<a href="/artists/System-Of-A-Down">System Of A Down</a>合作举办了一场一次性的联合头条演出 - 以下是发生的事情。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/deftones-white-pony-20-year-anniversary-interview-chvrches-fever-333-chino-radiohead-2692262">“这张唱片深深地印在我们的大脑中”：Deftones 的“White Pony”的无穷力量</a></strong></li></ul><p>周六（8 月 17 日），两支乐队占领了旧金山金门公园，大约有 50,000 名歌迷到场。 <a href="/artists/The-Mars-Volta">The Mars Volta</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Viagra-Boys">Viagra Boys</a>和 VOWWS 等乐队担任了该剧的开场表演。</p><p>这场演出是 System Of A Down 今年迄今为止唯一一场现场演出，除了今年 4 月份在拉斯维加斯举办的 Sick New World 音乐节上，他们的演出门票全部售完。</p><p> Deftones上台并表演了一场挤满了15首歌曲的套装，其中包括他们的热门歌曲，例如“ Be and and Drive（远远）”，“我自己的夏天（Shove It）”，“ Digital Bath”，“ Cherry Waves”和“变化（在苍蝇的房子中）”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="我自己的夏天（推开） - 旧金山deftones @ Golden Gate Park，CA，2024年8月17日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6OHfHeK6W3Y?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="7个字 -  Deftones @ Golden Gate Park，旧金山CA CA，2024年8月17日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kr2QlnvxTk4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h3> <strong>Golden Gate Park的Deftones玩了：</strong></h3><p> <strong>“安静和开车（远）”</strong><br /> <strong>“我自己的夏天（推它）”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;暴风雨&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“转向城市”</strong><br /> <strong>“钻石眼睛”</strong><br /> <strong>“数字浴”</strong><br /> <strong>“针头和销钉”</strong><br /> <strong>“樱桃波”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;feiticeira&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;洗剂&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“迷迭香”</strong><br /> <strong>“火箭滑板”</strong><br /> <strong>“变化（在苍蝇的房子里）”</strong><br /> <strong>“创世纪”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;7个单词&#39;</strong></p><p>下一天关闭的系统系统，并用“ Genodal humanoidz”开放，这是他们在2020年发行的两首曲目之一。他们的25首唱片套装看到了<a href="/artists/Serj-Tankian">Serj Tankian</a>和Co Co粉碎一些稀有的少数少数。杰克（Jack&#39;）标志着他们自2019年以来首次表演这首歌，“ Pluck”和“ Nown”，这是他们自2018年以来首次演出的歌曲。他们的演出还看到他们表演了诸如&#39;Byob&#39;，&#39;Byob&#39;，&#39;Chop Suey&#39;和&#39;毒性&#39;。</p><h3> <strong>Golden Gate Park的下降系统播放：</strong></h3><p> <strong>“种族灭性人类”（首次作为揭幕战）</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;套房&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“监狱歌”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;先生。 Jack&#39;（自2019年以来的第一次；带有“ Hezze” Interlude）</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;士兵方 - 简介&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;byob&#39;</strong><br />